      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/573559264_18077365385468694_3852366360640996048_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e35_p1080x1080_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=108&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc2MDYxMDA4MjIxMjE2NDUzNg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMC5oZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=jmbTpW6lQNsQ7kNvwGTC0us&amp;_nc_oc=AdoFkwj-lTcqaaMn6J6ETnkvjd0TXvVuBkwDpK3YNCfRPhEdGlofMHbdkZaPxKBlxWo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=3IBMcCAr0yNg-bQKsWJefQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzxccHsKfk3VQMHOHgJ1tadf6WBEHt5WjdiwPPVvYCAQQ&amp;oe=69CA1686" alt="Instagram billede fra @insecure__men" /></p><p><strong>@insecure__men</strong></p><p>A man for all seasons is out today. Its been a wild #journey thanks to fat possum records for trying their best, paul renaud and raf rundell for shaking down the extra sugar, jasbo macpahil and paul cardow for standing by.. enjoy the album if possible. Hail</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/573559264_18077365385468694_3852366360640996048_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e35_p1080x1080_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=108&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzc2MDYxMDA4MjIxMjE2NDUzNg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMC5oZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=jmbTpW6lQNsQ7kNvwGTC0us&amp;_nc_oc=AdoFkwj-lTcqaaMn6J6ETnkvjd0TXvVuBkwDpK3YNCfRPhEdGlofMHbdkZaPxKBlxWo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=3IBMcCAr0yNg-bQKsWJefQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzxccHsKfk3VQMHOHgJ1tadf6WBEHt5WjdiwPPVvYCAQQ&amp;oe=69CA1686" alt="Instagram billede fra @insecure__men" /></p><p><strong>@insecure__men</strong></p><p>A man for all seasons is out today. Its been a wild #journey thanks to fat possum records for trying their best, paul renaud and raf rundell for shaking down the extra sugar, jasbo macpahil and paul cardow for standing by.. enjoy the album if possible. Hail</p>]]></content:encoded>
